snippet: Roger Federer says he hopes to play for at least another two to three years and that his "mindset is for the long term" in assessing his tennis future....
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer says he hopes to play for at least another two to three years and that his "mindset is for the long term" in assessing his tennis future.

headline.main: Roger Federer Says He Hopes to Play '2 to 3 More Years'
headline.print_headline: Roger Federer Says He Hopes to Play '2 to 3 More Years'
